I'll help you preview the project without modifying any code. Let's navigate to the project directory, install dependencies, and start the development server to preview the project.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Terminal.run",
        "args": {
            "cmd": "cd /data/chats/pnm8pd/workspace/dashboard && ls -la"
        }
    }
]
```

Let's check the package.json file to understand the project structure and commands before proceeding:

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Editor.read",
        "args": {
            "path": "/data/chats/pnm8pd/workspace/dashboard/package.json"
        }
    }
]
```

Now I'll install the project dependencies and then start the development server to preview the dashboard:

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Terminal.run",
        "args": {
            "cmd": "cd /data/chats/pnm8pd/workspace/dashboard && pnpm install"
        }
    }
]
```

Now that the dependencies are installed, let's start the development server to preview the dashboard:

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Terminal.run",
        "args": {
            "cmd": "cd /data/chats/pnm8pd/workspace/dashboard && pnpm run dev"
        }
    }
]
```

Now that the development server is running, I'll use Terminal.preview to create a preview link for the dashboard:

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Terminal.preview",
        "args": {
            "tab_id": "00",
            "port": 5173,
            "proj_name": "dashboard"
        }
    }
]
```

The dashboard is now running and accessible. I've successfully:
1. Installed all the project dependencies with `pnpm install`
2. Started the development server with `pnpm run dev` 
3. Created a preview link that you can use to access the dashboard

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I've successfully set up the dashboard preview without modifying any code as requested. \n\nThe dashboard is now running and can be accessed at: https://dashboard-xsu1hd-pnm8pd-e89dc0.mgx.dev\n\nI used the following steps:\n1. Navigated to the project directory\n2. Installed dependencies with `pnpm install`\n3. Started the development server with `pnpm run dev`\n\nYou can now view and interact with the dashboard through the provided preview link."
        }
    }
]
```

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

